Full Description: Verbind is the leading supplier of real-time eMarketing solutions that empower firms to target customers, deliver messages, and build long-lasting profitable relationships with their customers. The end results are collaborative one-to-one personal interactive relationships on the basis of individual patterns of behavior. Verbind's real-time solution produces the most complete and timely information for targeting who, what and when to communicate most effectively. By synthesizing and evaluating offline and online interactions, monitoring activity and non-activity, and automatically sending messages when they are most relevant, companies are able to not only track when customer behavioral trends reveal business opportunities and threats, but are also able to reach the right customer with the right message at the right time. That means messages are automatically delivered when the window of opportunity opens, not after it's shut. Even if that window is open for only an instant. This solution helps marketers manage and maximize the lifetime value of each customer, by developing personal relationships with customers who communicate with them through historically impersonal means, such as via the Internet and call centers.

Description: Leverage Research supports scientific progress by studying early stage science and conducting exploratory social science research
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Leverage Research is a 501(c)(3) research institute that aims to support scientific progress by investigating how early stage science works, conducting our own exploratory social science research and supporting promising research projects. Leverage Research was founded in 2011 as an experiment to bring together researchers who were interested in figuring out how to improve the world. Researchers were encouraged to pursue their own research agendas with their own methods and form collaborations as they saw fit. They conducted investigations in many subdomains of epistemology, psychology, and sociology with varying degrees of success. Through trial and error we learned some surprising things about how to do early stage science. The Leverage Research team is now seeking to build on these initial insights by investigating historical examples of early stage science works, attempting to do early stage science ourselves, and support promising early stage research projects.
Industry Groups: Biotechnology, Health Care, Other, Science and Engineering, Social Impact

Bidcurement utilizes market research to identify the best suppliers, contractors, and products to ensure cost-effectiveness and quality of the infrastructure projects. Bidcurement provides a collaborative platform that enables organizations to work closely with suppliers and contractors to get the best value for their infrastructure projects. It helps to streamline procurement processes, reduces the risk of fraud, and ensures compliance with industry standards and regulations. Bidcurement is a powerful platform that helps organizations to manage their infrastructure projects efficiently and effectively while reducing the costs and risks associated with these projects.
